To use:

    git config core.hooksPath <this-directory>/hooks

Use `bin/nomis-cljfmt-v2-git-push` to push.

If we are using CLJS:

    brew install clojure # see https://clojure.org/guides/getting_started
    brew install planck # see http://planck-repl.org/setup.html

    ln -s <this-repo-root-directory> ~/nomis-git-stuff
